commentable_entity.description: Johnny Depp has been wrongly accused, he is innocent! There are audio recordings of the day in Australia when Amber heard accused Johnny of domestic and sexual violence when Johnny has stated Amber threw a vodka bottle at him and sliced off his fingertip subjecting him to a skin graft, infection, MRSA and much pain and suffering! Supposedly there is an ongoing FBI investigation of Amber Heard or alias names including Amber Van Ree or Larisa Vanda.
